21 SECTION 3. A NEW SECTION OF KRS CHAPTER 189 IS CREATED TO
22 READ AS FOLLOWS:
23 (1) Any person who violates subsection (2) of Section 2 of this Act shall be assessed a
24 civil fine of:
25 (a) Seventy-five dollars ($75) for the first violation; or
26 (b) One hundred twenty-five dollars ($125) for the second and each subsequent
27 violation within a three (3) year period.
